      <data key="d0">Pattern: If a student completes all online modules on a platform with 99% uptime, they master the course content. -&gt; ForAll(s, ForAll(c, (complete_modules(s,c) ∧ (uptime(c) ≥ 99)) → master_content(s,c)))</data>
