      <data key="d0">Pattern: If a student masters content in three courses but fails to submit capstone projects in any, they must take proctored exams for all three. -&gt; ForAll(s, ForAll(c1, ForAll(c2, ForAll(c3, (master_content(s,c1) ∧ master_content(s,c2) ∧ master_content(s,c3) ∧ ¬submit_capstone(s,c1) ∧ ¬submit_capstone(s,c2) ∧ ¬submit_capstone(s,c3)) → (take_exam(s,c1) ∧ take_exam(s,c2) ∧ take_exam(s,c3))))))</data>
