      <data key="d0">Pattern: If a student completes modules across four courses with 99% uptime and passes all exams, they qualify for an advanced credential. -&gt; ForAll(s, ForAll(c1, ForAll(c2, ForAll(c3, ForAll(c4, (complete_modules(s,c1) ∧ complete_modules(s,c2) ∧ complete_modules(s,c3) ∧ complete_modules(s,c4) ∧ (uptime(c1) ≥ 99) ∧ (uptime(c2) ≥ 99) ∧ (uptime(c3) ≥ 99) ∧ (uptime(c4) ≥ 99) ∧ pass_exam(s,c1) ∧ pass_exam(s,c2) ∧ pass_exam(s,c3) ∧ pass_exam(s,c4)) → advanced_credential(s))))))</data>
